statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `lop` inner join `khoa_hoc` on `lop`.`ma_khoa_hoc` = `khoa_hoc`.`ma_khoa_hoc` inner join `chuyen_nganh` on `lop`.`ma_chuyen_nganh` = `chuyen_nganh`.`ma_chuyen_nganh`

select *, (select count(*) from `sinh_vien` where ma_lop = lop.ma_lop) as `sy_so` from `lop` inner join `khoa_hoc` on `lop`.`ma_khoa_hoc` = `khoa_hoc`.`ma_khoa_hoc` inner join `chuyen_nganh` on `lop`.`ma_chuyen_nganh` = `chuyen_nganh`.`ma_chuyen_nganh` order by `ma_lop` desc limit 5 offset 0
